- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning algorithms to infer the phone's location.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of mobile platforms and applications.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper analyzes the power consumption of various components and applications on the phone.
